      <title>印度监管机构正在调查阿达尼是否违反信息披露规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/india-sebi-looking-into-whether-adani-flouted-disclosure-rule</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，印度资本市场监管机构正在调查阿达尼集团是否违反了强制披露市场动态信息的规定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/india-sebi-looking-into-whether-adani-flouted-disclosure-rule</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 07:32:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三菱日联银行解雇一名员工，因其从客户保险箱中盗窃 1300 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/mufg-fires-worker-for-13-million-theft-from-clients-safe-boxes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三菱日联金融集团表示，已解雇一名员工，该员工涉嫌从大约 60 名客户的保险箱中窃取高达 20 亿日元（1300 万美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/mufg-fires-worker-for-13-million-theft-from-clients-safe-boxes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 07:32:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称 Greatview 董事长正考虑与 Cloudview 进行竞标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/greatview-chairman-said-to-weigh-counterbid-with-cloudview</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，纷美无菌包装股份有限公司董事长正在与中国私募股权公司云景资本洽谈联手收购这家乳制品包装公司，此举可能会引发竞购战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/greatview-chairman-said-to-weigh-counterbid-with-cloudview</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 07:15:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
